title: WESTCOAST / GARY barks
description: Gary pretends to be doing something useful.

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""I'd take a bullet for you, but I w..."
dialogueTree.english: "I'd take a bullet for you, but I won't spend another hour out here."
dialogueTree.polish: „Mógłbym oberwać za ciebie kulkę, ale nie spędzę tu jeszcze jednej godziny”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Я мог бы атрымаць кулю за цябе, але не застануся тут яшчэ адну гадзіну».

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""Seeing if there are any signs of p..."
dialogueTree.english: "Seeing if there are any signs of phasmid activity. And taking a leak."
dialogueTree.polish: „Sprawdzam, czy nie ma tu żadnych oznak aktywności straszyka. I odlewam się”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Правяраю, ці няма тут ніякіх прыкмет дзейнасці прабачніка. І адліўваюся».

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""But everything's so... moist.""
